</div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:402px;"><a href="/wiki/File:PoFRotation.png" class="image" title="Figure 3. Rotation of the plane of focus."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4b/PoFRotation.png/400px-PoFRotation.png" width="400" height="297" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:PoFRotation.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
