<li><a href="http://cgi.cae.wisc.edu/~ram/Wiki/data/MyWork_attach/msthesis.pdf" class="external text" title="http://cgi.cae.wisc.edu/~ram/Wiki/data/MyWork_attach/msthesis.pdf" rel="nofollow">Unilateral Real-time Scheimpflug Videography to Study Accommodation Dynamics in Human Eyes</a> (PDF) by Ram Subramanian.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.bobwheeler.com/photo/ViewCam.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.bobwheeler.com/photo/ViewCam.pdf" rel="nofollow">Notes on View Camera Geometry</a> (PDF) by Robert Wheeler.</li>
